title: BaubleBar Teams Up With NFL
itunes:title: BaubleBar Teams Up With NFL
description:
Daniella Fiala, Co-Founder of BaubleBar, discusses the fast-fashion jewelry designer that specializes in accessories and their partnership with the NFL.

Hosts: Carol Massar and Sonali Basak. Producer: Paul Brennan.
